name: The Essie (Sofia Black/Downtown)
description:
An easy to carry clutch with enough room for all your essentials. The laid-back luxe look of the Essie will take you from day to night with ease. The chic utility foldover clutch features a zip top, two interior pockets, and a contrasting cotton lining.

Size

  • 11"w x 6.5"h (folded) 11"w x 10"h (unfolded)

Material

  • Linen with a cotton canvas lining

Details

  • Foldover clutch with zippered top and two interior pockets

Care Instructions

  • Do not machine wash or use bleach. Do not submerge.
  • Surface spots can be cleaned with water and a gentle cleanser. Do not submerge. If spot is not easily removed, consult a dry cleaning specialist.

name: The Nova (Primrose/Herringbone Indigo)
description:
Perfect to slip in your purse, overnight or gym bag, this zip-top catch-all is just right for your daily essentials. Coordinating fabrics make the Nova a great addition to our Quinn and Daytripper for a complete set and can moonlight on its own as a delightful and durable clutch.

Size

  • 9" l x 3" w x 6" h

Material

  • Laminated cotton exterior
  • Contrasting cotton fabric interior

Details

  • Pouch with zip top closure

Care Instructions

  • Do not machine wash or use bleach. Do not submerge.
  • Laminated exterior and interior lining can be easily wiped clean with a damp cloth.

name: The Quinn (Primrose/Herringbone)
description:
This go-anywhere shape features an open top and spacious interior to carry it all in our quintessential everyday tote.

Fashioned from vibrantly printed, laminated cotton, the exterior is pretty and practical. With a reinforced bottom and sturdy nickel hardware, the Quinn has the brawn and beauty to get you through whatever your day has in store!

Size

  • 14"l x 6"w x 12"h
  • drop length: 28"

Material

  • Laminated cotton exterior
  • Contrasting cotton fabric interior
  • Nickel hardware

Details

  • Over the shoulder bag with open top
  • Two interior pockets
  • Interior key hook

Care Instructions

  • Do not machine wash or use bleach. Do not submerge.
  • Laminated exterior and interior lining can be easily wiped clean with a damp cloth.

If what's on the inside counts, then put it in here! Meant to hold your mother lode of daily essentials, the Supernova will keep your beauty secrets safe. From makeup to lotions and potions, the durable laminated cotton is easy on the eyes to stand alone on your vanity or pair with the Daytripper to stow sunscreens and essentials.

Size

  • 10"l x 6"w x 8"h

Material

  • Laminated cotton exterior
  • Contrasting cotton fabric interior

Details

  • Pouch with zip top closure

Care Instructions

  • Do not machine wash or use bleach. Do not submerge.
  • Laminated exterior and interior lining can be easily wiped clean with a damp cloth.

name: The Essie (Keely)
description:
An easy to carry clutch with enough room for all your essentials. The laid-back luxe look of the Essie will take you from day to night with ease. The chic utility foldover clutch features a zip top, two interior pockets, and a contrasting cotton lining.

Size

  • 11"w x 6.5"h (folded) 11"w x 10"h (unfolded)

Material

  • Lightweight cotton canvas with a cotton canvas lining

Details

  • Foldover clutch with zippered top and two interior pockets

Care Instructions

  • Do not machine wash or use bleach. Do not submerge.
  • Surface spots can be cleaned with water and a gentle cleanser. Do not submerge. If spot is not easily removed, consult a dry cleaning specialist.

name: Lovey (Giverny in Aqua)
description:
Soft as a baby’s bottom, this incredibly plush baby blanket is sure to become your little one’s favorite companion. Silky, soft pile is finished on both sides and trimmed in colorful cotton to make the perfect snuggle companion.

Size

  • 40"l x 31"w

Material

  • This extraordinary soft and cuddly fabric has a smooth minky surface
  • 100% polyester

Details

  • Plush blanket

Care Instructions

  • Machine wash with a gentle cleanser on a gentle cycle. Do not dry clean or machine dry. Line dry. Porter & Plum will not be responsible for items dry cleaned or machine dried.
